             was indicted for <rs id="t17820410-9-off50" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17820410-9-off50" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17820410-9-off50" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17820410-9-cd51" type="crimeDate">18th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17820410-9-off50 t17820410-9-cd51"></join> last, one silver tankard, value 6 l. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17820410-9-victim196" type="victimName">
                           Hans 
                           Stonys
                        <interp inst="t17820410-9-victim196" type="surname" value="Stonys"></interp>
